492
00:40:12,160 --> 00:40:12,520
 Aha.

493
00:40:12,520 --> 00:40:14,900
 I nisam otvoren za ništa drugo.

494
00:40:14,900 --> 00:40:17,980
 Znači, ta osoba mora biti taka, taka, taka

495
00:40:17,980 --> 00:40:19,420
 i mora imati to, to, to i to.

496
00:40:19,420 --> 00:40:23,200
 I to je jedna od najčešćih grešaka.

497
00:40:23,200 --> 00:40:25,440
 Opet ću se navratiti na onaj dio priče

498
00:40:25,440 --> 00:40:27,620
