 baš tako.

745
00:46:58,380 --> 00:46:58,760
 Znači,

746
00:46:58,760 --> 00:47:00,060
 imamo li tu nekih

747
00:47:00,060 --> 00:47:01,060
 predivnih

748
00:47:01,060 --> 00:47:02,880
 ili možda još malo boljih

749
00:47:02,880 --> 00:47:03,400
